    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;RFC-904 is the specification of the Exterior Gateway Protocol (EGP).  This memo updates portions of RFC-888 and RFC-827.  This RFC specifies an official protocol of the DARPA community for use between gateways of different autonomous systems in the ARPA-Internet.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
